Story

After two years of hard training, the Straw Hat pirates are back together, first at the Sabaody Archipelago and then through Fish-Man Island to their next stage: the New World!!
Luffy and crew defeat Doflamingo, then get through a scuffle with Big Mom, an Emperor of the Sea, on their way to Wano for the purpose of taking down Kaido. The lead party of Robin, Usopp and Franky have been undertaking

clandestine work to prepare for the coming battle. Then Kaido shows up in the form of a great dragon and attacks the crew. A furious Luffy attacks him but loses and gets sent to an excavation labor camp. The rest of the group focuses on recruiting allies for the big battle and freeing Luffy from prison. Meanwhile, Robin gets invited to Orochi's palace with Komurasaki the Oiran. She engages in some intelligence gathering until she's spotted by Orochi's followers and trouble ensues!!
